{"tid":2015394,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣演員柯宇綸: 中國不要再欺負「香港」","createTime":"2020-05-13T15:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T09:26:12.000Z","uid":134071,"like":76,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"33bb1e7371dbd7dbef06005181c3c71103e318be","tid":2015394,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"柯宇綸早前因「被台獨」而被中共封殺, 亦令由他與梁朝偉合演的中港合拍片《風再起時》被中共禁演. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n而家, 柯宇綸話佢並不盡支持台獨, <strong>而是支持中國獨立, 自立自強, 不要再欺負「香港」.</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp; (由7:44開始睇)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/abC3MPGyGzE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FabC3MPGyGzE&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=ebfb49eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/abC3MPGyGzE</a>"},{"pid":"9c669fa778ca17419575eb8beee1c51ee4b57c6e","tid":2015394,"uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T15:52:29.000Z","msg":"值得一提, 柯宇綸話以前香港電影片酬高過《色，戒》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n柯宇綸話佢演出由王晶監製的香港電影《愈快樂愈墮落》, 片酬有40萬台幣.<br />\n<br />\n反而, 柯宇綸係幾年後演出李安導演《色，戒》, 套戲拍左八個月, 但片酬只有20萬台幣. (雖然劇組係每個拍攝日都向柯宇綸給予100港元的膳食費.) 但柯宇綸唔後悔, 因為可以換到八個月時間向李安學習.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aAH7B_sOL-c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaAH7B_sOL-c&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=035944ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aAH7B_sOL-c</a>"},{"pid":"a4587dc50ea25bff8fe1a32919af499d410c18dd","tid":2015394,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T15:52:45.000Z","msg":"台灣手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703350307155db455a6690475b1b60e470b21a